    stream close() method throws an error.

    We want the speculative parsing to just try another path.

    The unparse will not even utilize the layer because the branch
    in the parse result is the one without the layer in it.
    -->
    <document>A</document>
    <infoset>
      <dfdlInfoset>
        <ex:root2 xmlns="">
          <data>A</data>
        </ex:root2>
      </dfdlInfoset>
